          </div>


        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bio">
        <h2>BIO</h2>
        <p>Previously working in architecture, pivoting into the tech industry, leveraging a strong foundation in design and problem-solving. Thriving under strict deadlines and driven by client-specific requests, I have honed my ability to deliver exceptional results while maintaining a strong attention to detail. Passionate about coding, I started on a self-taught journey and recently completed a 9 week intensive coding bootcamp to further enhance my technical skills.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="projects-container primary-border">
      <h2>PROJECTS</h2>
      <div class="project-card primary-border underline-div">
        <div class="card-title">
          <h3 class="underline">BarHop</h3>
          <h6>Le Wagon, 2023</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="more-info">
          <div class="project-images">
            <%= image_tag ("barhop/homepage.jpg") %>
            <%= image_tag ("barhop/indexpage.jpg") %>
            <%= image_tag ("barhop/generate_route.jpg") %>
            <%= image_tag ("barhop/routes.jpg") %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="project-card primary-border">
        <h3 class="underline">Render</h3>
        <h6>Le Wagon, 2023</h6>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
